item.title: By: jennc
item.dc:creator: jennc
item.description:
I don't know how I found this post. (Was looking at software? Or an app or something? And got linked here maybe?)
Regardless, your post, your perfect post, helped me to communicate with my husband just what the hell this effing depression is like. For that, I thank you.
Sending you rest and whatever you might need to help you surface soon.
jc
